description: Located in the heart of the city! Beautiful view of cathedral of learning from top floor bedroom. Convenient location minutes from UPMC Childrens, Shadyside and West Penn hospitals. Close to The Strip District, Lawrenceville & Shadyside communities with famous shops, restaurants, museums and more. Walk to Aldi grocery, local shops & restaurants as well! Updated throughout this spacious 4 bedroom 2 full bath home offers a open concept main floor. Highlights include a large entryway, picture window perfect for holiday decorating and gourmet kitchen with oversized island and pot filler for the stove. Upstairs are 4 generously sized bedrooms and full bath. The owner’s suite features double closets and a private full bath with double vanity. Hard to find fenced in backyard space with patio and upper deck. Plenty of yard for cookout or pet paradise. City living at it’s best don’t miss this one, huge equity potential over the next few years in booming Garfield area.
